{
  "texts": [
    "7 For this reason, our subsequent analysis uses encouragement as the primary workplace treatment.",
    "AI chatbots are reshaping the nature of work.",
    "Among chatbot users with employer initiatives, about 12% report new tasks from chatbots (Table 1, Column 8).",
    "These tasks include both productive activities (e.g., content drafting, ideation) and non-productive ones (e.g., integration, compliance, oversight).",
    "Appendix B.3 classifies this new work using workers' free-text descriptions."
  ]
}